sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant Controller
    participant ExceptionHandler
    participant ErrorReportAspect
    participant ErrorReporter
    participant LlmErrorReporter
    participant ErrorAnalyzer
    participant SlackNotifier
    participant Redis

    Client->>Controller: API 요청
    Controller-->>ExceptionHandler: 예외 발생
    
    %% Exception Handling & AOP Trigger
    ExceptionHandler->>ErrorReportAspect: @After(ExceptionHandler)
    ErrorReportAspect->>ErrorReporter: report(ex, request)
    ErrorReporter-)LlmErrorReporter: report(ErrorAnalysisRequest) [Async]
    
    %% Return Error Response (Main Thread)
    ExceptionHandler-->>Client: 에러 응답 (ex: 400/500)
    
    %% Async Error Analysis & Reporting (Worker Thread)
    Note over LlmErrorReporter: 비동기 스레드에서 실행 (@Async)
    LlmErrorReporter->>Redis: setIfAbsent(cacheKey, NOTIFY_DURATION)
    Redis-->>LlmErrorReporter: 에러 캐싱 여부 반환 (isLockSuccess)

    alt 에러 캐시 (isLockSuccess = true)
        LlmErrorReporter->>ErrorAnalyzer: analyze(request)
        ErrorAnalyzer-->>LlmErrorReporter: ErrorAnalysisResponse 반환
        LlmErrorReporter->>SlackNotifier: send(message)
        LlmErrorReporter->>Redis: set(cacheKey, TRUE, NOTIFY_DURATION) [쿨타임 갱신]
    else 에러 키 이미 존재 (isLockSuccess = false)
        Note over LlmErrorReporter: 에러 중복 분석 방지 (Return)
    end